Module org.microbean.interceptor
Package org.microbean.interceptor

Interface Prioritized

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<Prioritized>
All Known Subinterfaces:
InterceptorFunction
public interface Prioritized extends Comparable<Prioritized>
An interface indicating that its implementations can supply an int indicating a relative priority (smallest number wins; "quality is job one"; "first place"; "X is your first priority").

Note particularly that a negative priority trumps a positive one.

Author:
Laird Nelson
